# T1105 Ingress Tool Transfer — certutil download
alert http any any -> any any (msg:"LAB T1105 Possible certutil cache fetch pattern in URI"; flow:to_server; content:"GET"; http_method; content:".exe"; http_uri; content:"/download"; http_uri; sid:9105502; rev:1; classtype:trojan-activity; metadata:mitre_technique T1105;)

# Path traversal / scanning (web exploit scenario)
